<?xml version="1.0" encoding="big5"?>
<root>
<name>% (modulo) 餘數</name>

<category>Math</category>

<subcategory>Operator</subcategory>

<usage>網路及應用程式</usage>

<example>
<image></image>
<code>
int a = point(30, 20%100);   // Sets a to 20%100 = 20
int b = point(85, 520%100);  // Sets b to 520%100 = 20
int c = point(85, 75%100);   // Sets c to 75%100 = 75
int d = point(30, 275%100);  // Sets d to 275%100 = 75
</code>
</example>

<description>
計算某值被另一值除後的餘數。適用於把數字限制在指定的範圍中，例如把形狀限制在螢幕的象限內。
</description>

<syntax>
<c>value1</c>%<c>value2</c>
</syntax>

<parameter>
<label>value1</label>
<description>整數</description>
</parameter>

<parameter>
<label>value2</label>
<description>整數</description>
</parameter>

<returns></returns>

<related>
/ (divide)
</related>

<availability>1.0</availability>

<type>Operator</type>

<partof>PDE</partof>








</root>
